episodes.title: Inside the Brethren: Secretive church opens its doors
episodes.description:
After decades of negative media stories, members of the secretive Plymouth Brethren Christian Church with just 16,000 members have spoken for the first time. 

Read the exclusive interview with Dean and Charles Hales: https://bit.ly/4mOqLor
